    "Following this intuition, we can update the user input feature matrix as follows:Z ℓ+1 = 𝑫 𝑣 -1 2 𝑼 𝑯𝑾 𝑫 𝑒 -1 𝑯 T 𝑼 𝑫 𝑣 -1 2 X ℓ 𝚯 (5)where 𝚯 is the layer-specific trainable parameters, ℓ = 0, • • •, 𝐿 denotes the hypergraph neural network layer.",
